{"type":"message","id":"e522a4a4","parentId":"1e9817b2","timestamp":"2026-03-01T17:03:46.905Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_64eab109f1d3416faf608468","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: polymarket-paper\ndescription: \"Polymarket模拟交易系统 - 用虚拟资金学习交易策略\"\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"emoji\":\"📈\",\"homepage\":\"https://polymarket.com\"}}\n---\n\n# Polymarket 模拟交易系统\n\n## 功能\n- 虚拟资金池 ($10,000起始)\n- 市场监控与机会识别\n- 策略执行 (TAIL/BONDING/SPREAD)\n- 绩效追踪 (胜率/盈亏比/夏普比率)\n- 历史回测\n\n## 触发词\n- \"模拟交易\"、\"paper trade\"\n- \"查看绩效\"、\"performance\"\n- \"运行策略\"、\"run strategy\"\n- \"回测\"、\"backtest\"\n\n## 安全\n- 不需要私钥\n- 不执行真实交易\n- 仅分析市场数据"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772384626903}}
